e_Beroricthena = {
	color = { 0 0 0 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

e_Gyrthkuae = {
	color = { 158 216 31 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }
	capital = c_Nympdidyai

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score

		}

e_Liserythuf = {
	color = { 50 50 50 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }
	capital = c_Arsadramios

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

	k_Lefkmorgrias = {
		color = { 204 248 134 }

		capital = c_Moacantherna

		can_create = {
			NOT = {
				faith = {
					religion_tag = christianity_religion
					has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
				}
			}
		}

		ai_primary_priority = {
			if = {
				limit = {
					culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
				}
				add = @correct_culture_primary_score
